query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('apex',
'beginner',
'java',
'javascript',
'magento-1.9',
'magento2',
'marketing-cloud',
'performance',
'php',
'python',
'python-3.x',
'trigger')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Benefactor',
'Enlightened',
'Enthusiast',
'Explainer',
'Necromancer',
'Peer Pressure',
'Promoter',
'Quorum')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('codereview',
'magento',
'salesforce')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
